    {
      "id": "standard_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "standard_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in poor condition. The exterior has significant scratches, dents, and paint damage across multiple panels. The interior shows heavy wear including torn upholstery, damaged trim, and worn surfaces throughout. Mechanical issues are present and will likely require attention. Priced accordingly for a buyer comfortable with a project vehicle or repairs.",
      "price": 6000.0,
